Renee Olstead https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Renee_Olstead 0 Renee Olstead (born June 18, 1989) is an American actress and singer. Active since childhood as an actress, she is best known for her roles on the CBS sitcom Still Standing and on the drama The Secret Life of the American Teenager as Madison Cooperstein. In addition, she has recorded four studio albums, primarily of jazz music. Renee_Olstead ( born June_18_,_1989 ) is an_American_actress_and_singer .
